text: Dempo Sports Club is a football club from Panaji, Goa, India. The club is owned and sponsored by the mining company Dempo. They won 5 league titles more than any other club in India. ==Honours== *I-League: 3 ::2007–08, 2009–10, 2011–12 *National Football League: 2 ::2005, 2007 *Durand Cup: 1 ::2006 *Federation Cup: 1 ::2004 ==References== Category:Indian football clubs Category:Goa
title: Dempo SC
